description=<p>The latest release of J!WHMCS Integrator, version 2.4 has been restructured and reconfigured for greater flexibility and control.  Among the improvements of version 2.4:</p><ul><li>Merging of Joomla! 1.5 and Joomla! 2.5 into a single package</li><li>In-application product updates and checks - never miss an update again!</li><li>Refactoring of the WHMCS side - JWHMCS now utilizes the WHMCS Addon Module method of installation and management.</li><li>Template overrides - no longer necessary to duplicate your WHMCS template directory structure with jwhmcs-classic, jwhmcs-default, jwhmcs-portal directories.</li></ul><p>Be sure to check upgrade and installation instructions prior to install.</p><p>Important note:  J!WHMCS Integrator 2.4 is no longer backwards compatible with WHMCS version 4.</p><p><strong>Important Note:</strong> The WHMCS portion of the package requires PHP version 5.3 or higher to be installed for use on WHMCS version 5.2.1!</p>
